you may try to know me.

275
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:14,870
What kind of men do you like?

276
00:31:20,130 --> 00:31:23,540
Knowing a person doesn't mean
you’ll be able to win his love.

277
00:31:23,630 --> 00:31:25,670
A person changes.

278
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:28,590
He may like pineapples today,

279
