295
00:36:59,290 --> 00:37:01,580
Two more minutes and I'll be 25.

296
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:07,120
In other words. I've lived a quarter of a century.

297
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:12,040
To celebrate this historical moment,

298
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,890
I go jogging

299
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:18,150
to get rid of the excessive water in my body.

300
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:22,110
This makes me feel very happy.

301
00:37:23,080 --> 00:37:26,770
