405
00:52:18,410 --> 00:52:21,990
Can you give this to him when you see him?

406
00:52:23,420 --> 00:52:25,420
No problem.

407
00:52:25,420 --> 00:52:27,450
Thank you.

408
00:52:51,070 --> 00:52:52,690
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

409
00:53:57,910 --> 00:53:59,730
I've to go out for a while.

