00:53:59,910 --> 00:54:02,410
- What?
- I've to go out for a while.

411
00:54:02,410 --> 00:54:04,450
OK....

412
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:07,740
We have to go out for a while.

413
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:08,920
What?

414
00:54:08,920 --> 00:54:11,080
